<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc9dd2dd-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s361"><num value="361">§ 361.</num><heading> Publication of recommendations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The recommendations of the President which take effect shall be printed in the Statutes at Large in the same volume as public laws and shall be printed in the Federal Register and included in the Code of Federal Regulations.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc9dd2de-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/206/tII/s225/k">Pub. L. 90–206, title II, § 225(k)</ref>, <date date="1967-12-16">Dec. 16, 1967</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/81/644">81 Stat. 644</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="iddc9dd2df-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="iddc9dd2e0-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="iddc9dd2e1-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1967-12-16">Dec. 16, 1967</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/90/206/s220/a/1">section 220(a)(1) of Pub. L. 90–206</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s3110">section 3110 of Title 5</ref>, Government Organization and Employees.</p>
</note>
</notes>
